Tenders for making of the desks were awarded by President Uhuru Kenyatta mid this year.
Speaking in Embu, the prelate also appealed to the government to extend assistance to private schools, saying many are struggling following the closure in March, and some may not even re-open.
Help private schools
Bishop Kariuki noted that private schools play a key role in the education sector and should be assisted to stay afloat so as to help ease congestion in public schools.



